{"tid":2084330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲籍手足喺獄中畫咗幅畫畀大家","createTime":"2020-06-29T07:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T08:04:52.000Z","uid":19501,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0625b76c0dee4d7fda65758d36309e9fff19875","tid":2084330,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"澳洲籍女子被指掟磚囚三個月　獄中書信勉堅持五大訴求　信正義必勝<br />\n<br />\n報道全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3g002U2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3g002U2&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=39158aa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3g002U2</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲籍女子 Rebecca Louise Nunan，去年 11 月 12 日「三罷」期間，被指在中環交易廣場行人天橋上向警方投擲磚頭，但沒有傷及仼何人，承認企圖襲警判監三個月，社福界立法會議員邵家臻在 fb 貼出她的書信和畫作，鼓勵港人堅持五大訴求、缺一不可，「Justice must prevail, one day!」<br />\n<br />\nRebecca 在畫作中，畫了一名長髮帶頭盔眼罩的女示威者，和代表五大訴求缺一不可的手勢，她在信中指，非常感謝外界對她的鼓勵，支持她渡過在獄中的黑間歲月，指她畫這幅畫，是表達政權可以剝奪自由，但不能夠消滅信念，相信正義一定會得勝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Ofvuf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Ofvuf4.jpg&h=16fcefa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8106fc78d6349c3db5381f13544b9b09e4b786c8","tid":2084330,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25b3656a9bd7deeaf567af86698917fa245e122","tid":2084330,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"手足啲畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/beccarexart?igshid=1udscm5whs56m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fbeccarexart%3Figshid%3D1udscm5whs56m&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=73f57b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/beccarexart?igshid=1udscm5whs56m</a><br />\n<img src=\"https: